    "content": "<h2>Objem</h2>\n<p><strong>Objem</strong> je fyzikální veličina, která vyjadřuje, kolik prostoru těleso zaujímá. Značíme ho <strong>V</strong>.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 360 220' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <text x='100' y='20' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='13'>Odměrný válec</text>\n  <path d='M60,30 L60,200 Q60,210 80,210 L120,210 Q140,210 140,200 L140,30' fill='none' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <rect x='62' y='100' width='76' height='108' fill='#93c5fd' opacity='0.4'/>\n  <path d='M62,100 Q100,95 138,100' fill='none' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <line x1='55' y1='50' x2='65' y2='50' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='50' y='54' text-anchor='end' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>100</text><line x1='55' y1='75' x2='65' y2='75' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='50' y='79' text-anchor='end' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>75</text><line x1='55' y1='100' x2='65' y2='100' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='50' y='104' text-anchor='end' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>50</text><line x1='55' y1='125' x2='65' y2='125' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='50' y='129' text-anchor='end' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>37</text><line x1='55' y1='150' x2='65' y2='150' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='50' y='154' text-anchor='end' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>25</text><line x1='55' y1='175' x2='65' y2='175' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='50' y='179' text-anchor='end' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>12</text>\n  <text x='42' y='210' fill='#374151' font-size='9'>0 ml</text>\n  <line x1='145' y1='100' x2='200' y2='80' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='1' stroke-dasharray='3'/>\n  <text x='210' y='78' fill='#ef4444' font-size='11'>odečítáme zde</text>\n  <text x='210' y='92' fill='#ef4444' font-size='11'>V = 50 ml</text>\n  <text x='280' y='150' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='12'>Kvádr</text>\n  <path d='M240,165 L310,165 L310,200 L240,200 Z' fill='#dbeafe' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <path d='M240,165 L260,150 L330,150 L310,165' fill='#bfdbfe' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <path d='M310,165 L330,150 L330,185 L310,200' fill='#93c5fd' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='275' y='210' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>V = a · b · c</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Jednotky objemu</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Jednotka</th><th>Značka</th><th>Převod</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>metr krychlový</td><td>m³</td><td>základní jednotka</td></tr>\n<tr><td>decimetr krychlový</td><td>dm³</td><td>1 dm³ = 0,001 m³</td></tr>\n<tr><td>centimetr krychlový</td><td>cm³</td><td>1 cm³ = 0,000001 m³</td></tr>\n<tr><td>litr</td><td>l</td><td>1 l = 1 dm³</td></tr>\n<tr><td>mililitr</td><td>ml</td><td>1 ml = 1 cm³</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Měření objemu</h3>\n<p><strong>Kapaliny:</strong> odměrný válec — odečítáme na spodním okraji menisku.</p>\n<p><strong>Pravidelná tělesa:</strong> výpočet (kvádr: $$V = a \\cdot b \\cdot c$$).</p>\n<p><strong>Nepravidelná tělesa:</strong> ponořením do vody v odměrném válci — objem tělesa = rozdíl hladin.</p>"
  }
}
